    >
        <div class="container-custom">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <div
                    class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-primary/10 to-brand-blue/10 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-white/10 p-10 md:p-16 text-center"
                >
                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tight"
                    >
                        Why <span class="text-brand-primary">Subscribe?</span>
                    </h2>
                    <p
                        class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-medium italic mb-10"
                    >
                        Fresh data + continuous updates = better results, every
                        single month.
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="text-left space-y-6 text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto border-t border-white/10 pt-10"
                    >
                        <div class="flex gap-4">
                            <span
                                class="text-2xl text-brand-primary flex-shrink-0"
                                >📈</span
                            >
                            <div>
                                <p class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">
                                    Monthly Fresh Leads
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    Your B2B leads list grows every month with
                                    newly verified prospects. No data decay, no
                                    stale contacts.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-4">
                            <span
                                class="text-2xl text-brand-primary flex-shrink-0"
                                >🤖</span
                            >
                            <div>
                                <p class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">
                                    AI Agents Get Smarter
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    Our AI marketing agents are continuously
                                    trained. Monthly improvements mean better
                                    automation and higher conversion rates.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-4">
                            <span
                                class="text-2xl text-brand-primary flex-shrink-0"
                                >🔄</span
                            >
                            <div>
                                <p class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">
                                    Always Updated Platform
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    New features, security patches, and
                                    performance improvements delivered
                                    automatically. Stay ahead of the curve.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-4">
                            <span
